{
  "texts": [
    "Finally, the Latency (ms) metric reflects the inference time of the model, including the time required for model forward propagation and post-processing.",
    "This metric facilitates the evaluation of the algorithm's realtime performance and applicability.",
    "In the preparation stage, we employed data augmentation strategies including Mosaic 49 and Cutout 50.",
    "The input images were resized to 1280 × 1280 and necessary padding was applied.",
    "Instead of traditional Adam, we used the recently released Lion 51 optimizer."
  ]
}